Charts.Name: Detected Malwares in Last 7 Days
Charts.CommandText: SELECT        dbo.Date(Net_Rpt_Threats.ReceivedTime) AS Date_ReceivedTime, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM            Net_Rpt_Threats                      WHERE        (7 >= DATEDIFF(DD, Net_Rpt_Threats.ReceivedTime, GETDATE()))                      GROUP BY dbo.Date(Net_Rpt_Threats.ReceivedTime)                      ORDER BY 1

Charts.Name: Padvish Version Status
Charts.CommandText: SELECT        dbo.[bi.AbrvType](Type)  + ' ' +  dbo.[AbrvValue](ProductVersion,'.',2) AS Abrv_Type_ProductVersion, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM            Net_Clients                      GROUP BY dbo.[bi.AbrvType](Type)  + ' ' +  dbo.[AbrvValue](ProductVersion,'.',2)                      ORDER BY 2 DESC

Charts.Name: Client Protection Status
Charts.CommandText: SELECT  Net_Rpt_Clients.Status AS Net_Clients_Status, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM         Net_Rpt_Clients                      GROUP BY Net_Rpt_Clients.Status                      ORDER BY 2 DESC

Charts.Name: Padvish License Usage
Charts.CommandText: SELECT        dbo.[bi.AbrvType](Net_Rpt_Licenses.Type) AS Abrv_Type, SUM(AllocatedLicense)-SUM(UsedLicense) AS SUM_1, SUM(UsedLicense) AS SUM_2                      FROM            Net_Rpt_Licenses                      GROUP BY  dbo.[bi.AbrvType](Net_Rpt_Licenses.Type)                      ORDER BY 1

Charts.Name: Client Management Status
Charts.CommandText: SELECT  Net_ClientDiscovery.Status AS Net_ClientDiscovery_Status, COUNT(*) AS COUNT                      FROM         Net_ClientDiscovery                      GROUP BY Net_ClientDiscovery.Status                      ORDER BY 2 DESC
